    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>enchiladas</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, with the seams facing down</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>over the top</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 10-12 min or until the cheese is golden and melted – these are your <strong>vegetable enchiladas</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to use 2 dishes!</p>",
